Victor Millan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Millan 0 Victor Millan, whose real name was Joseph Brown, (August 1, 1920 – April 3, 2009) was an American actor, academic and former Dean of the theatre arts department at Santa Monica College in Santa Monica, California. Victor Millan was Brown's pseudonym used during his acting career, which spanned decades.
